data.description: Discover your dream home in Dayton, TN! This charming ranch boasts an open floor plan, beautiful hardwood floors, a granite counter tops in the kitchen, and a serene mountain view. The primary bedroom offers an ensuite, while the heated and cooled garage with insulation creates the perfect workspace. Enjoy the fenced backyard in a great subdivision, complete with additional parking space. Contact me for a viewing!
